Piers Flint-Shipman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Piers_Flint-Shipman 0 Piers Fredrick Alexander Flint-Shipman (23 January 1962–2 June 1984) was a British actor. He was the son of film producer Gerald Flint-Shipman and was educated at Eton College. Piers_Fredrick_Alexander_Flint-Shipman ( 23_January_1962 – 2_June_1984 ) was a_British_actor .
